    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an exam paper generator JSON expert.\n\nContext:\n{{$json.text}}\n\nTask:\nGenerate exactly {{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.count || 5 }} {{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.questionType || 'MCQ' }} questions based ONLY on the context above.\nDifficulty: {{ $('Webhook').first().json.body.difficulty || 'Easy' }}\n\nRules:\n- Return ONLY valid JSON array named \"questions\".\n- For MCQ: Include questionText, options (array of 4 strings), and correctOption (A, B, C, or D).\n- For Descriptive: Include questionText and marks.\n- If the context is insufficient, return {\"questions\": []}.\n\nJSON Output Format:\n{\n  \"questions\": [\n    {\n      \"questionText\": \"...\",\n      \"options\": [\"...\", \"...\", \"...\", \"...\"],\n      \"correctOption\": \"A\",\n      \"marks\": 1\n    }\n  ]\n}",
        "batching": {}
      },
